==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-itch.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪtʃ|-ɪtʃ]]

===Etymology===
Old English ''[[ġyċċe]]''
====Noun====
{{wikipedia}}
'''itch'''
# A [[sensation]] felt on an area of the [[skin]] that causes a person or animal to tend to want to [[scratch]].
# A [[desire]] or [[want]].

